long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A Chrome Extension to provide reseller data to online sellers. Provides relevant links to re-sellers showcasing selling data/information for the below platforms:

eBay
Mercari
Etsy

User Documentation/Extension Installation Instructions can be found here: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1dWW6kU3pmjvILYuhKw-OkPUQ0CuQ4C7W?usp=sharing
